		Course Book Editor, ALFA International 2008 Product Liability Practice Group Seminar, Beyond the Horizon….A New Dawn for Global Product Liability Claims (2008)

		Course Book Editor, ALFA International 2007 International Client Seminar, Shifting Sands of Global Product Liability Issues (2007)

		Successor Liability in Virginia, Journal of Civil Litigation Vol. X, No. 4 (1998)



