About
Ward Michael R Dds is located at the address 375 Bullard Ave Ste 3 in Clovis, California 93612.  They can be contacted via phone at (559) 298-7424 for pricing, hours and directions.  Ward Michael R Dds specializes in Sleep Disorders, Aches & Pains, Cosmetic Dentistry.  Ward Michael R Dds has an annual sales volume of 0 - 500K.  .For more information contact Michael R  Ward, Ward Michael R Dds provides Root Canals, X-Rays, Bonding to it's customers.  For maps and directions to Ward Michael R Dds view the map to the right.  For reviews of Ward Michael R Dds see below.









